<section class="hero">
  <h1>Your <em>Bitcoin Deployment Plan</em></h1>
  <div class="hero-subtitle">You have money to put into Bitcoin. Deploy it all now, ladder in, or do some of each?</div>
  <p class="subtitle">Model your own plan &mdash; your sum, your cadence, your time horizon &mdash; see how it would have fared historically, and how it might fare over the years ahead.</p>
</section>

<main class="content-area">

