    <div class="dp-takeaway" id="dpBackstopTakeaway"></div>

    <div class="dp-prose" style="max-width:none; margin-top:2rem;">
      <p>And the edge from timing has been shrinking anyway: Bitcoin&rsquo;s swings have compressed cycle over cycle, so it increasingly lives low-to-mid channel where decisiveness wins. The clever &ldquo;wait for the top to pass, then ladder down&rdquo; move is one you rarely get to use anymore. Maximum channel position reached, by four-year window:</p>
